    <h1>Cloaking</h1>
    <p class="description">A black-hat SEO technique that shows different content to search engines than to users. It violates Google's Spam Policies and triggers <strong>manual actions</strong> that can remove the entire domain from search.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
