        <p>theStacc's technical audit performs user-agent parity checks on every important URL, cross-references Googlebot rendering against human rendering, and flags any content divergence. If a manual action has already landed, we scope the cleanup and draft the reconsideration request. Delivered in 24 hours.</p>

